T02TD3093E:188a-1: 'khrul 'khor snga ma ltar brgyad byas te /
T02TD3093E:188a-2: tha mar ser ba'i 'byung po m'a ra ya bandha ya nan /
T02TD3093E:188a-3: bya ba bkod nas bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor byas nas /
T02TD3093E:188a-4: phyag rgya'i tshogs kyis bkug bcings nas /
T02TD3093E:188a-5: kham phor ram thod par bcug nas /
T02TD3093E:188a-6: bsrung bar bya ba'i yul gyi phyogs mtshams bzhir dong gru gsum du snga ma ltar mnan te /
T02TD3093E:188a-7: tsha tsha btabs nas mchod rten brgyad byas te /
T02TD3093E:188a-8: de gzungs 'di bris te mchod cing bskor ba byas nas gzhag ba dang /
T02TD3093E:188a-9: yungs kar la sngags 'bum la sogs pa bzlas te gzhag pa dang /
T02TD3093E:188b-0: gzhan du yang @188b bskor ba dang tshangs pa la sogs pa la gtor ma byin te /
T02TD3093E:188b-5: yul de'i lha dang klu la sogs pa la mchod pa dang gtor mas tshim par byas nas gsol ba gdab bo //
T02TD3093E:188b-6: de nas gzungs la rtag tu mchod cing bzlas pa dang /
T02TD3093E:188b-7: skabs su mchod pa dang gtor ma gtang zhing sprin la sogs pa byung ba'i tshe bdag nyid lha'i nga rgyal byas te thams cad 'joms pa bzlas shing yungs kar dang bcas pa nam mkha' thams cad phyag rgya'i tshogs kyis gdabs 'joms par bsam mo //
T02TD3093E:188b-8: ser ba srung ba'i thabs rdzogs so//
